All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
eWordle
The eWordle class stores the default settings and launch the game.
Game
The Game class manages a game window that enables user to play the game and shows the result window after the game ends.
Results
The Results class manages a result window that enables user to see the result and choose whether to restart or go back to settings.
Service
The Service class loads words from Trimmed.csv and stores indexes of those words, providing all the functionalities related to word sources.
Settings
The Setting class manages a setting window that enables user to configure preferences and start the game via creating a new Game instance.
